org.apache.paimon.table

Interface Table

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DataTable, FileStoreTable, InnerTable, ReadonlyTable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AggregationFieldsTable, AllTableOptionsTable, AuditLogTable, BranchesTable, BucketsTable, CatalogOptionsTable, ConsumersTable, FileMonitorTable, FilesTable, ManifestsTable, OptionsTable, PartitionsTable, PrivilegedFileStoreTable, ReadOptimizedTable, SchemasTable, SinkTableLineageTable, SnapshotsTable, SourceTableLineageTable, StatisticTable, TableLineageTable, TagsTable

    @Public
public interface Table
extends Serializable
    A table provides basic abstraction for table type and table scan and table read.
    Since:
    0.4.0
